#O  TriangulizedIntegerMat(<mat>[,<trans>])
#O  TriangulizedIntegerMatTransform(<mat>[,<trans>])
#O  TriangulizedIntegerMatInverseTransform(<mat>[,<trans>])
##
##  The first operation computes an upper triangular form of a matrix
